title: BATTLE OF THE LOST TEMPLE: FREE FOR ALL - Total War: Warhammer 2 Gameplay
description:
Total War: Warhammer 2 is so close to release and to celebrate we have a 4 player free for all. YES! That's right Free for all is back! I will be leading the Skaven, IndyPride will be commanding the High Elves, Party Elite controls the Lizardnew, and Alex the Rambler leads the Dark Elves. Four armies march to the battlefield, but only one will be left standing! Enjoy the video :D

Battle Buddies:
PartyElite: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg3BiSs8eBE9hA9EWYTgtAg
IndyPride: https://www.youtube.com/user/milkandcookiesTW
AlexTheRambler: https://www.youtube.com/user/therambler146


JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
